==制作==
由于2011年女性喜剧片《[[伴娘我最大|伴娘我最大]]》的成功，导演决定继续拍摄女性主角的喜剧片<ref>{{cite web|last=Kohen|first=Yael|title=It's Kind of a Funny Story|url=http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity-lifestyle/celebrities/its-kind-of-a-funny-story-the-heat|publisher=[[Marie_Claire|Marie Claire]]|accessdate=June 27, 2013|page=3|date=April 3, 2013|archive-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227052020/http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity-lifestyle/celebrities/its-kind-of-a-funny-story-the-heat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片是凯蒂·迪波尔特编剧的首部电影，此前她一直担任电视剧的编剧<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title=‘The Heat’ Scribe Katie Dippold Makes 7-Figure Sale To Chernin Entertainment|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/the-heat-scribe-katie-dippold-makes-7-figure-sale-to-chernin-entertainment/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=June 27, 2013|date=April 3, 2013|archive-date=2014-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619141249/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/the-heat-scribe-katie-dippold-makes-7-figure-sale-to-chernin-entertainment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年7月在波士顿取景开拍<ref>{{cite web|title=‘The Heat’ with Sandra Bullock begins filming in Dudley Square|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/2012/07/05/the-heat-with-sandra-bullock-and-melissa-mccarthy-begins-filming-dudley-square/DsnXCzbXz2CXO5Gmi7VAKN/story.html|publisher=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|accessdate=June 27, 2013|author=Mark Shanahan|coauthors=Meredith Goldstein|date=July 6, 2012|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303031517/https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/2012/07/05/the-heat-with-sandra-bullock-and-melissa-mccarthy-begins-filming-dudley-square/DsnXCzbXz2CXO5Gmi7VAKN/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 迴响 ==
美国首周末收获3911万美元，美国最终票房为1.59亿，加上国际市场累计2.29亿，成为年度票房第二高的喜剧片，仅次于2.69亿的《[[冒牌家庭|冒牌家庭]]》。

在口碑方面也不错，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度达66%，两位主演的喜剧表演普遍得到认可；[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上37家媒体评分为60分。

